# JMB Printing Services - Membership Form (v2.0)

This HTML form auto-generates a Loyalty Card Number (LCN) and QR Code based on the user's full name.

## Features
- Logo header and version control
- Auto-generated LCN: (YY-JMBPS-GivenName,MiddleName,LastName-00000)
- Real-time QR code based on LCN
- Digital and physical card claim dates noted
- Clean and printable layout

## How to Use
1. Open the file in any modern browser.
2. Enter your first name, middle name, and last name.
3. LCN and QR code will auto-generate.
4. Print or save as needed.

## Requirements
- Internet access (for QRious QR code library)
- logo.png (provide your logo and name it `logo.png`)

